About Us
Monthly or long term RV rentals available on Timber Island in the heart of Carrabelle, Florida. Vista views of Dog & St. George Island, The Carrabelle River and Apalachicola Bay.

Minutes to the Gulf of Mexico, for the best in fresh and salt water fishing. Jet ski, canoe, kayak, birding, hiking…a true nature lover’s paradise!
Normal page content
Our History
Sunset Isle began as an exclusive waterfront community with two phases. Phase 1 lots #1-23 located next to the Carrabelle River side of Timber Island as homes only and Phase 2 lots #24-56, located on the Apalachicola Bay side of Timber Island as RV lots, build now or later.
Our Vision
Celebrating our tenth year in business! We started with a goal to make your stay with us everything you were looking for and more! A place to relax, have fun, a place where strangers become friends. A place you want to visit again and again!
Our Services
We aim to please…from guide fishing, guided tours…just ask us, we will hook you up!
RV Site Rentals (50 amp service)

Family Fun!
From sunrise to sunset, Sunset Isle offers something for everyone to enjoy. Monthly and long term rentals only beginning 1/1/2022.
